{
  "texts": [
    "A \"no pain-no gain\" poster on a gym wall may be regarded both as a mood-regulating artifact in Piredda's sense, making athletes more determined, and a motivational one in Viola's sense, nudging athletes to keep training.",
    "As this example shows, the two taxonomies are not mutually exclusive.",
    "Indeed, Piredda's feeling-regulating artifacts and Viola's feeling artifacts are overlapping categories.",
    "In fact, the taxonomies can be used at once, to gain a deeper understanding of affective artifacts.",
    "Importantly, both taxonomies are functional taxonomies: they focus on what affective artifacts do."
  ]
}